quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Ndithudi Ife tidamupatsa kale chilangizo Abrahamu ndipo tinali kumudziwa bwino
  21,52,"Pamene Iye adawauza abambo ake ndiponso anthu ake kuti, “Kodi mafano amene muli kuwapembedzawa ndi chiyani?”"
  21,53,"Iwo adati, “Ife tidapeza makolo athu ali kuwapembedza.”"
  21,54,"Iye adati, “Ndithudi inu ndiponso makolo anu mwakhala muli kuchimwa kwambiri.”"
  21,55,"Iwo adati, “Kodi ndi zoona zimene wadza nazo kwa ife kapena ndi nthabwala chabe?”"
  21,56,"Iye adati, “Iyayi. Ambuye wanu ndi amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndipo muzimenezo ine ndichitira umboni.”"
  21,57,“Ndilumbira pali Mulungu kuti ine ndidzachita chiwembu pa mafano anu inu mukangochoka.”
  21,58,Motero iye adaziphwanya zonse kukhala tizidutswa kupatula fano lalikulu kuti akhoza kudzalifunsa
  21,59,"Iwo adati: “Kodi ndani amene wachita izi kwa milungu yathu? Ndithudi iye ali oipitsitsa.”"
  21,60,"Iwo adati, “Ife tinamva mnyamata wotchedwa Abrahamu akunena za milunguyo.”"
  21,61,"Iwo adati, “Mubweretseni pamaso pa anthu onse kuti achitire umboni.”"
  21,62,"Iwo adati, “Kodi iwe ndi amene wachita izi ku milungu yathu? Oh Abrahamu!”"
  21,63,"Iye adati, “Iyayi. Ndi uyu, wamkulu kuposa zonse amene waziphwanya. Afunseni, ngati angayankhule”"
  21,64,"Pamenepo iwo adayang’anizana okha nati, “Ndithudi inu ndinu anthu ochimwa kwambiri.”"
  21,65,"Ndipo adayang’anizananso nati, “Ndithudi iwe uli kudziwa kuti milungu iyi siiyankhula.”"
  21,66,"Abrahamu adati, “Kodi inu mumapembedza mowonjezera pa Mulungu zinthu zimene sizingathe kukuthandizani chilichonse kapena kukuonongani?”"
  21,67,“Tsoka likhale pa inu ndi pa mafano anu amene mumapembedza kuonjezera pa Mulungu! Kodi mulibe nzeru?”
  21,68,"Onse adati, “Mutentheni kuti muteteze milungu yanu ngati mufuna kuchita china chilichonse.”"
  21,69,"Ife tidati, “Iwe moto khala wozizira ndi wamtendere kwa Abrahamu.”"
  21,70,Ndipo iwo adafuna kumuononga Iye koma Ife tidawapanga iwo kukhala olephera
  21,71,Koma Ife tidamupulumutsa iye pamodzi ndi Loti ndipo tidawaika ku dziko limene tidalidalitsa kuti zolengedwa zonse zikhalemo
  21,72,Ndipo Ife tidamupatsa Isake ndi Yakobo ngati chidzukulu chake ndipo tidawapanga onse kukhala anthu angwiro
  21,73,"Ndipo Ife tidawasankha iwo kukhala atsogoleri olangiza anthu ku ulamuliro wathu ndipo tidawalamulira kuti azigwira ntchito zabwino ndipo, azipitiriza kupemphera ndi kupereka zothandizira osauka. Ndipo iwo anali kutitumikira Ife nthawi zonse"
  21,74,"Ndi Loti tidamupatsa luntha, utumiki ndi nzeru za chipembedzo ndipo tidamupulumutsa ku mzinda umene anthu ake anali kuchita zoipa. Ndithudi, iwo anali anthu ochita zoipa ndipo anali osamvera Mulungu"
  21,75,"Ndipo Ife tidamulowetsa m’chisomo chathu, ndithudi, iye adali mmodzi wa anthu olungama"